&lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.bis.gov.uk/assets/biscore/consumer-issues/docs/c/12-1193-civil-enforcement-remedies-consultation-on-extending.pdf"&gt;Civil enforcement remedies: consultation on extending the range of remedies available to public enforcers of consumer law (PDF, 440 Kb) &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.bis.gov.uk/assets/biscore/consumer-issues/docs/c/12-1193rf-civil-enforcement-remedies-consultation-on-extending-form.doc"&gt;Civil enforcement remedies: consultation on extending the range of remedies available to public enforcers of consumer law. Response form (DOC, 145 Kb) &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.bis.gov.uk/assets/biscore/consumer-issues/docs/c/12-1194-civil-enforcement-remedies-impact-assessment.pdf"&gt;Civil enforcement remedies: extending the range of remedies available to public enforcers of consumer law. Impact assessment (PDF, 257 Kb) &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
