  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.bis.gov.uk/assets/biscore/enterprise/docs/i/12-1132-impact-directive-on-combating-late-payment.pdf"&gt;Impact assessment: Directive of the European Parliament and the Council on Combating Late Payment (PDF, 195 Kb) &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
